Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.44,0:01:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏是三增卡山的山腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於要真正的挑戰登山了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:44.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過大家為什麼對目的地要保密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.29,0:01:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是個什麼石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,額 是達磨石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:56.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒翁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不倒翁先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}日語中達磨和不倒翁一個念法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它上面寫著什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梵字aaH 是指大日如來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像寫了什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山上沒有垃圾箱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.57,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(628,412)} {\an8}登山這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三增卡標高是多少呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是1786米吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尾山好像是599米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是它的3倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 但是 這路比想像中更容易走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且到處都有長凳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 長凳是不是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:56.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定會很容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要看？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:06.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看 從那棵分成兩股的樹幹中間看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有美麗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美麗的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 快走吧 太陽要下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我們加緊吧 小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前路漫漫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:23.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大家突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 就像近在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 能看到日向…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一次要爬的山決定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.32,0:03:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地點保密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 這是驚喜？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我之前說想看富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你在幹什麼呢 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.42,0:03:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之裝作不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得日向為我計劃了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定這前面還會有更棒的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下馬點？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}山路變得險阻 必須從所乘之馬上下來的地點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬還能到這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬兒 真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坡好像陡起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難怪說馬也回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位小心點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斜坡很陡 全是岩石很難走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的時間變得越來越長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕快跟上大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腳也痛 背包也沉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難受 我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會來這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想在長凳上休息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才還有那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一個都沒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.19,0:05:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.32,0:05:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 是不是太努力了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也難怪 畢竟有獎品富士山在等著你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經注意到驚喜是什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還為了日向裝作沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是這麼溫柔的小葵也想回家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登山呢 和馬拉松一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度提高得太快 馬上就會累了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.90,0:06:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要保持速度 累了就休息一會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃點甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累的時候甜食最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先掰開放進袋子裏 馬上就可以吃到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不會製造垃圾 很方便的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 不愧是楓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.17,0:06:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息完恢復精神再繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的按照自己的速度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步幅小一點比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:56.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是苦著臉大家都會掃興的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 所以楓一直都是面帶笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是有點勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然開始爬真正的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.61,0:07:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當辛苦的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵 要不要試試用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是折疊滑雪杖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個呢 這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.38,0:07:34.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對在山路上保持平衡也很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:42.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,步幅變小 每走一步都要注意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山呢 雖然一開始在森林裏什麼都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登啊登啊 穿過森林的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定有美麗的景色在等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:56.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到那個的時候 我總是在想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒放棄真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒在等你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能只是走的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來不要急 慢慢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫的是八十八大師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.97,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵也喝喝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼 好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從樹縫間透過的陽光非常舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然還是很難走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過感覺很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想快點向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.64,0:09:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 但是不能急 要慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山崖？要通過這裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.77,0:09:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掉下去的話絕對沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:20.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只看著地面走走看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:31.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像日向說的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看周圍 只看著腳下前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 不怎麼害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣應該就能走過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.86,0:09:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 慢慢走 慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了 已經安全了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧 什麼事都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.90,0:10:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回頭看看 還是一樣的可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一步一步前行 總能到達的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:02.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山 真的像畫裏一樣藍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我也能看到這樣的景色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比照片之類的看起來更漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為我是一路靠自己的雙腳走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道你在路上就注意到驚喜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟那個沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的謝謝你
